## What is this?

This is an **ADE (Agent Dev Environment)** — a Cursor workspace scaffolded from a [copier template](https://github.com/madi-parloa/ade-template). It contains:

- A portfolio of Parloa infrastructure repos listed in `ade-repos.txt` (cloned by copier `_tasks` during initial `copier copy` only).
- GSD (Get Shit Done) installed workspace-locally for spec-driven development (on initial scaffold only).
- The `claudes-kitchen/` and `open-kitchen/` repos cloned as reference source. Their setup scripts are NOT auto-run — they mutate user/system state (see `claudes-kitchen/setup-cooking-environment.sh`). Run them manually if you want global installation.
- Pre-seeded codebase intelligence in `.planning/codebase/` so GSD is immediately Parloa-aware.

## Quick start

This ADE was created with:

```bash
uvx copier copy --trust git+https://github.com/madi-parloa/ade-template.git <this-directory>
```

## Updating from the template

Pull latest template/docs changes (new AGENTS.md guidance, updated `.planning/codebase/*` intel, refreshed workspace file):

```bash
uvx copier update --trust
```

`copier update` is a pure template/docs refresh. It does NOT re-sync the portfolio or reinstall GSD.

## Re-syncing the portfolio (manual)

If you added or removed lines in `ade-repos.txt` (or `copier update` brought in new portfolio entries from the template), clone/pull manually:

```bash
while read -r url; do
  dir="$(basename "$url" .git)"
  [ -d "$dir" ] || git clone "$url" "$dir"
done < <(grep -Ev '^\s*(#|$)' ade-repos.txt)

for d in */; do [ -d "$d/.git" ] && git -C "$d" pull --ff-only; done
```

## Refreshing GSD

```bash
npx -y get-shit-done-cc@latest --local --cursor
```

## Producing a different ADE

1. **Different repos** — re-run copier with `--data portfolio_file=/path/to/my-repos.txt`, or edit `ade-repos.txt` and sync manually (see above).
2. **Fork the template** — `gh repo fork madi-parloa/ade-template --remote` and scaffold from your fork.

## Files

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `AGENTS.md` | Agent-level workspace context (what repos are here, conventions, guardrails) |
| `CLAUDE.md` | Claude-specific instructions |
| `ade-repos.txt` | Git URLs of repos to clone |
| `.planning/PROJECT.md` | GSD project definition |
| `.planning/codebase/*.md` | Pre-seeded codebase intelligence |
| `.cursor/` | Workspace-local Cursor config (populated by copier `_tasks` / GSD on first scaffold) |
